| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-3769 — Recovery Inhibition (ransomhouse)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 85830c26-7b42-5315-b5b2-28ca1bc33fb3"
